data.description: Wait until you See this HOME!!  4 Bedroom , 2 Full bath, 2 Car Garage , Brick ranch , sits on .5 acre fenced beck  lot . Immaculate Upgraded Expansive Kitchen with  Stainless Appliances, Island, Breakfast nook, Pantry, and Updated Lighting . Large Living Room with Built Ins, Dining , Updated Bathrooms, 2 Bedroom on the Main and 2 Bedrooms In Lower Level along with A Large Family/ Rec Room, and Great Sized laundry and Storage . Newer Modern  Flooring updates  throughout this home, no carpet in this home. Within the past year ~ Seller has replaced all Windows and Doors , including the Garage Door  with  wifi Opener . Seller has also installed Solar Panels . He has also added blown insulation into the attic . New A/C with Heat Pump .
